attr.title: Gato Roboto
attr.desc: Pounce inside of your cozy armored mech and set off on a dangerous trek through an alien underworld full of irritable creatures and treacherous obstacles in a valiant effort to save your stranded captain and his crashed spaceship.
attr.inst: Install port. Download the windows version of game on Steam or GOG. Copy all gamefiles to the gamedata folder.
attr.inst_md: Install port. Download the windows version of game on [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/916730/) or GOG. Copy all gamefiles to the gamedata folder.
